Here's a complete breakdown of every feature Inform Direct UK offers — nothing skipped.

**What it is:** Inform Direct is award-winning, cloud-based company secretarial software that currently supports compliance for more than 450,000 companies throughout the UK. It's used by business owners, directors, and accountants.

Here's a quick summary of each section in the visual above:

**Company Formation** — Form new limited companies directly with Companies House, check name availability instantly, and get auto-generated documents the moment incorporation is complete.

**Officers (Directors & Secretaries)** — Appoint, resign, or update any officer. Inform Direct is a web-based service that enables you to maintain your own company records online. Whenever you make a change, Inform Direct will automatically update the relevant registers and determine whether the details also need to be submitted to Companies House.

**PSC Register** — Add, update, or cease Persons with Significant Control. From 18 November 2025, for newly appointed PSCs, the personal code must be supplied at the time the PSC is notified to Companies House. Inform Direct supports this new requirement.

**Shares & Shareholders** — Handle allotments, transfers, consolidations, sub-divisions, share options, dividend vouchers, and certificates — all with auto-updated registers.

**Statutory Registers** — A full suite of compliant registers for companies limited by shares, guarantee companies and LLPs. As you make changes in Inform Direct, the appropriate registers will be updated automatically.

**Companies House Filings** — Inform Direct takes you step by step through any changes and electronically submits the data to Companies House once you confirm the changes. The clever software also suggests documents that may be required to support your transaction.

**Document Library** — It can produce over 400 different documents, including template board minutes and resolutions, company letters, forms and certificates, pre-populated with the information you entered, so you won't need to enter it all again.

**Portfolio Management** — Manage all your companies from one dashboard, import existing companies in under a minute, and receive automated deadline reminders.

**User Management** — Invite team members and control their access rights and permissions.

**Security** — Inform Direct is a cloud-based system — your data is stored in a high-security UK data centre. 256-bit SSL/TLS technology is used to encrypt all data between you and their servers.

**Pricing** — PAYG is cost-effective for up to 10 companies with many features free to use. Subscription gives unlimited access to the entire system for a single monthly payment based on the number of companies you manage.